{"tid":2224902,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"3C東主母家書：堅持才有希望","createTime":"2020-10-01T02:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T02:07:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3febc76beaed369ec801735f09eac7afd34cbfb6","tid":2224902,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T02:07:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/PXXPRJE4YZFUTPZGMPET5PMD6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FPXXPRJE4YZFUTPZGMPET5PMD6U%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyh3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=6ab41741\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FPXXPRJE4YZFUTPZGMPET5PMD6U%2F&h=5c851933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/PXXPRJE4YZFUTPZGMPET5PMD6U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n3C東主母家書：堅持才有希望<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/j7YbdJjPLAKuaTc9ZauDXPGVJTk=/2103x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XBYTIXRLNZGVROWPRIKTSPT7UE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fj7YbdJjPLAKuaTc9ZauDXPGVJTk%3D%2F2103x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXBYTIXRLNZGVROWPRIKTSPT7UE.jpg&h=79be5dcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■母親寫下家書，為兒子打氣。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中秋節本是人月兩團圓的節日，惟早前遭國安處拘捕並正收押的黃店「3C維修工作室」東主賴振邦（阿邦），其家人今年只能愴然面對圓月。據知阿邦曾因情緒不穩有自殺念頭，年邁的母親接受本報專訪並寫下家書鼓勵阿邦振作：「有堅持才有希望，家人一定撐你！」<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n阿邦家人接受本報訪問，年邁的媽媽眉頭緊鎖，不發一言。直至問及今年中秋會如何度過時，她始垂淚表示，由於兒子不在家，一直擔心其安危，心情沉重，已經沒有過節打算。「今年中秋係好特別嘅一年，特別黑暗。」<br />\n<br />\n阿邦在收押所內曾有尋死念頭，他一直心繫母親，日前更特地寫信叮嚀：「呢幾日入夜開始凍，會寒寒地（哋），你自己着多件衫，希望可快啲出返嚟。」阿邦媽媽寫下家書鼓勵：「你一定要撐住，有堅持才有希望，家人一定撐你，媽媽唔會放棄&hellip;&hellip;你要好好珍惜自己。在家時你有媽煲的湯，但離家不知你怎樣&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hv9EOsbSuvPTA7KQZYAQPU8PKcw=/1165x728/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JFTGJKQ7RZAWDM6GQFU6TI6QXM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fhv9EOsbSuvPTA7KQZYAQPU8PKcw%3D%2F1165x728%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJFTGJKQ7RZAWDM6GQFU6TI6QXM.jpg&h=6d03f93f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■阿邦胞姊表示，現時最大盼望是弟弟順利保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n收押所外伴度中秋<br />\n<br />\n阿邦媽媽日前在阿邦案件提堂時，曾不顧一切追着囚車大叫「阿邦，加油呀！」阿邦胞姊更抱住稚子、拖着幼女，到法庭支持。阿邦媽媽哽咽指：「畀警察上門搞咗好多次，𠵱家每逢有人敲門我就好驚，仔女擔心我心臟出事。但我要堅強，阿仔係我希望，我哋今年冇得團圓，但希望佢會撐住，保留有用之軀。我哋一家會喺收押所出面陪住佢，以另外一個形式同佢一齊過中秋，希望大家唔好唔記得咗佢。」<br />\n<br />\n阿邦胞姊亦傷心指，阿邦為家中經濟支柱，月初突然被國安處拘捕不准保釋，現時家中經濟頓失靠依，財政緊絀。「3C維修工作室」亦因阿邦不在，只能維持有限度服務，並暫時遣散店內部份員工。「阿邦現時最大盼望是可以順利保釋，靜待昭雪一天。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qsv91WAUcdphAYQk_zGCLX_sTSY=/493x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Y7GQHIPKZ5FUDBP7CDO5OD2RAI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fqsv91WAUcdphAYQk_zGCLX_sTSY%3D%2F493x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FY7GQHIPKZ5FUDBP7CDO5OD2RAI.jpg&h=e3316875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■3C東主上月初被警登門拘捕。"}]}